This paper is about natural language parsing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also describes a machine learning approach using spectral learning, which is a subfield of both machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of multiple models and decoding strategies, which are related to data science (cs.DS) and search algorithms (cs.SD).
